        <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> You are responsible for ensuring your site meets all applicable laws (consumer law, e-commerce regulations, accessibility, cookie and privacy rules, and so on).</li>
        <li><strong>Content &amp; claims:</strong> You are responsible for the accuracy and legality of your product descriptions, pricing, offers, and claims (including health, income, or performance claims).</li>
        <li><strong>No guarantees:</strong> We do not guarantee specific results such as traffic, sales, conversions, or search rankings.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="td-clause" id="branding">
